## Critical Rules

1. **Single source of truth:** Edit `directives/SOP.md` or `.agent/hints/`, then run `python tools/sync_configs.py`
2. **Never hand-edit** generated files: `CLAUDE.md`, `AGENT.md`, `GEMINI.md`, `.cursorrules`, `.claudecode.md`
3. Run `python tools/verify_{{DOMAIN}}.py` before completing any task

## Quick Commands

| Command | Purpose |
